11:32.792 --> 11:34.594 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: First time ever.

11:34.627 --> 11:40.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Once the
president-elect, then
