JUDY WOODRUFF: Or should they,
thinking you
need to fill that vacancy on the
court, go

11:50.510 --> 11:52.211 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
along?

11:52.245 --> 11:55.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: I think they
should -- look,
the Constitution says the
president shall

11:55.181 --> 12:00.887 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
