some other

13:01.481 --> 13:02.915 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
things.

13:02.949 --> 13:06.786 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But -- so, I'm not prepared to
comment on
any one of his nominees.

13:06.819 --> 13:12.158 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Come back to
foreign policy.
