the intelligence

13:12.191 --> 13:14.327 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
community on Russian hacking of
the Democrats
during the...

13:14.360 --> 13:16.963 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Yes, I have. Yes,
I've read
it.

13:16.996 --> 13:18.798 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And?

13:18.831 --> 13:24.637 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JOSEPH BIDEN: There's
overwhelming consensus
in the community and
overwhelming evidence

13:24.671 --> 13:31.511 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
