evidence that they
-- in fact, they were engaged in
activities

13:41.954 --> 13:44.891 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
designed to try to impact on the
outcome of
the election.

13:44.924 --> 13:49.395 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Evidence of any
American cooperation
with the Russians in doing that?

13:49.429 --> 13:52.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: I'm not going to
comment on
that, Judy. I don't want to
comment on any

13:52.532 --> 13:56.602 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the detail of the report.
There will be
an unclassified version that
will be released

13:56.636 --> 14:01.841 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
very shortly, and it will lay
out in bold
print what they know.

14:01.874 --> 14:04.243 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Will the American
people learn
something new from this?

14:04.277 --> 14:13.519 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: I think it will
probably confirm
what a lot of the American
people think.

14:13.553 --> 14:20.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But it will -- it will state
clearly that
the Russians did, as a matter of
policy, attempt

14:20.827 --> 14:31.003 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to affect and -- three things.
One, it attempted
to discredit the U.S. electoral
process by

14:31.037 --> 14:36.709 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
implying that or laying the
foundation for,
it is not on the level.

14:36.743 --> 14:44.684 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Two, it -- there's evidence that
they -- there
was an attempt to hurt Mrs.
Clinton. But there's

14:44.717 --> 14:52.091 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
also evidence that there was
wider hacking
than some people thought.

14:52.125 --> 15:00.867 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the idea that the Russians
were not involved
in an effort to engage in our
electoral process

15:00.900 --> 15:04.370 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
is simply not able to be
sustained. They were.

15:04.403 --> 15:05.338 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

15:05.371 --> 15:07.206 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Excuse me.

15:07.240 --> 15:11.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In connection with that, the
criticism by
the president-elect of the
intelligence community

15:11.144 --> 15:15.448 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in this country, belittling of
the intelligence
community, do you think that's
just politics,

15:15.481 --> 15:17.150 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
