15:17.183 --> 15:19.852 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: I think it's
dangerous.

15:19.886 --> 15:28.461 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I hope -- some very smart people
around him,
like General Mattis and some
others. For a

15:28.494 --> 15:41.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
president not to have confidence
in, not to
be prepared to listen to the
myriad of intelligence

15:41.140 --> 15:49.882 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
