Intelligence, to the
CIA, et cetera, is -- is
absolutely mindless.

15:49.916 --> 15:52.518 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's just mindless.

15:52.552 --> 15:57.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How would you -- now, can you
disagree? Can
you ask for more detail? Can you
question

15:57.857 --> 16:02.128 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
whether or not there is a
disagreement among
the various intelligence
agencies? That's

16:02.161 --> 16:04.030 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
