16:04.063 --> 16:12.205 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the idea that -- that you
know more than
the intelligence community
knows, it's a little

16:12.238 --> 16:16.576 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like saying, I know more about
physics than
my professor. Now, I didn't read
the book.

16:16.609 --> 16:18.411 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I just know I know more.

16:18.444 --> 16:24.517 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, it's not a -- it's
worrisome. I'm
assuming it will change.

16:24.550 --> 16:29.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: If -- if what the
Russians
did is so serious, should there
be more retaliation

16:29.155 --> 16:31.624 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
