expelling...

16:59.852 --> 17:00.820 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That were
announced.

17:00.853 --> 17:02.088 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Yes.

17:02.121 --> 17:02.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Will we know
those things that
weren't...

17:03.022 --> 17:05.157 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Hope not.

17:05.191 --> 17:12.098 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Syria, will that
go down as
one of the administration's
great failures,

17:12.131 --> 17:16.869 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
