now impotent
to affect the outcome there?

17:16.903 --> 17:19.372 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOSEPH BIDEN: No. No.

17:19.405 --> 17:28.047 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
