the -- there was -- you would
assume there

17:28.080 --> 17:33.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
was an alternative that could
have been offered
that would have benefited or
been great -- in

17:33.152 --> 17:37.657 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
