security of the
United States.

17:37.690 --> 17:41.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you notice, there wasn't
anybody in either
political party ever talking
about putting

17:41.394 --> 17:48.134 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
