Nusra, and take

18:33.980 --> 18:38.551 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
on the Assad regime at the same
time.

18:38.584 --> 18:46.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so our focus has been the
dismantling
of the so-called caliphate, the
dismantling

18:46.559 --> 18:54.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of ISIS being able to occupy
territory and
govern like they were a
nation-state, like

18:54.633 --> 18:56.669 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
