dismantled. It
will still be a problem, but
that has been

19:13.919 --> 19:17.456 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
our focus, because that is the
greatest existential
threat to U.S. interests.

19:17.490 --> 19:20.226 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And the
president, President
Assad, will still be in power?

19:20.259 --> 19:22.962 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: That remains to be
seen.

19:22.995 --> 19:27.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And why I say that is, we've
been saying from
the beginning, like most others,
that this

19:27.099 --> 19:34.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
