Assad being in
power indefinitely is not in
their interests.

19:47.319 --> 19:54.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, it remains to be seen. We've
been trying
to put together, in multiple
fora, ability

19:54.393 --> 20:01.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to bring a negotiated settlement
to this.
It's still a reach, but we'll
see.

20:01.067 --> 20:09.308 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
