20:37.002 --> 20:42.208 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The reason I'm a Democrat is
because the essence
of the Democratic Party is an
abhorrence for

20:42.241 --> 20:47.913 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
