got through.

20:50.716 --> 20:55.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I remember going -- I was flying
to Cleveland.
I did 83 events. I was flying to
Cleveland.

20:55.087 --> 20:59.692 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
