never got
to it. And...

21:19.578 --> 21:21.080 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Whose fault was
that?

21:21.113 --> 21:23.382 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Well, I think it
was the -- I
think it was multiple faults.

21:23.415 --> 21:27.052 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I don't think that the campaign
was clear
enough. I don't think you guys
were ready

21:27.086 --> 21:32.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
