at what the
Annenberg School and other
studies have shown,

21:32.591 --> 21:36.428 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
there's hardly any coverage of a
single issue,
of a substantive issue.

21:36.462 --> 21:38.264 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But you also said
the campaign
wasn't clear enough.

21:38.297 --> 21:41.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Well, I don't
think -- I've
been the odd man out here.

21:41.267 --> 21:46.772 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I -- you know, I didn't hear
anybody talk
about the plight of that guy who
works on

21:46.805 --> 21:50.843 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
