scared.

21:53.646 --> 21:59.318 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We don't show enough respect. We
don't show
enough. We don't speak enough to
-- my dad

21:59.351 --> 22:03.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
