it. We never
got to them.

22:14.233 --> 22:15.801 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Could you have
beaten Donald
Trump?

22:15.834 --> 22:18.671 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Oh, I don't --
