knows whether

22:24.677 --> 22:26.412 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I could have beaten Donald
Trump.

22:26.445 --> 22:28.514 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But you're seeing
-- seem very
clear on what the message should
have been.

22:28.547 --> 22:29.548 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN: Oh, I -- I was...

22:29.582 --> 22:30.816 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

22:30.849 --> 22:33.352 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
